data.meta_description:
MythCraft Playtest 03 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. 1. MythCraft was created by Grant Mielke and others and published by QuasiReal Publishing. 
2. The document outlines the terms of the Powered by MythCraft license, which allows creators to freely adapt and create derivative works using MythCraft content with certain conditions.
3. Creators must include attribution to QuasiReal Publishing and retain any original copyright notices. Derivative works are not required to have an open license but open licensing is encouraged. Failure to comply with the terms may result in legal action.
